==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Noncondensing
<hw>Non`con*dens"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Steam Engine)</fld>
<def>Not condensing; discharging the steam from the cylinder at a
pressure nearly equal to or above that of the atmosphere and not into a
condenser.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nonconducting</ent>⟦br⟧
